    "body": "This behavior is expected and it also occurs on 2.1.4 (I just tested it). When you ask for sync committee duties for the current epoch (or a later one), we retrieve the state at slot 0 of the current epoch as part of processing. When you issue the request very early in an epoch, the head state hasn't been updated yet, and that's why you get this error. If there's a missing block at slot 0, you will see this error throughout the whole slot.",
